  "title": "没有内斗，Meta 也没能留住 PyTorch 之父",
  "url": "https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzA3MzI4MjgzMw==&mid=2651000503&idx=2&sn=b7dc24f23e7583bf7e099c9bc031ca7d",
